    narr:narration """This hub gathers two unlike strands under one roof. The bulk is a cluster of style observations on how strategic prose is constructed: [anaphoric repetition](narr:StyleObs_Anaphora) for emphasis, [bold Title Case labels](narr:StyleObs_BoldLabels) signaling executive register, [em-dash arrow cadence](narr:StyleObs_BulletCadence) that mimics slide-deck logic in prose, and [parallel numbered failure progression](narr:StyleObs_FailureProgression) building toward a breakthrough. Cutting across these is a lone operational commitment — [content/newsletter as a re-engagement tool](narr:Narrative_ContentAsReengagement), a Ghost blog to warm leads with a one-week launch pledge. Read together, the style children describe a recognizable rhetorical register (executive-summary, deck-like, momentum-driven), while the re-engagement child is a concrete go-to-market action rather than a craft observation. No dates are attached to any child, so there is no trajectory to report; the grouping is thematic, not sequential.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ContentAsReengagement> ;
